## Architecture

This service follows hexagonal architecture (Ports & Adapters):

```
cmd/                    ← entrypoint only
internal/
  domain/               ← pure business logic, no framework imports
  infrastructure/       ← adapters: DB, cache, messaging, HTTP clients
  presentation/         ← inbound adapters: HTTP handlers
  app/                  ← application services, orchestration
```

## Company Standards (Non-Negotiable)

- All HTTP responses use RFC 7807 error format — never return raw error strings
- All log entries use structured JSON via `slog` — never `fmt.Println` or `log.Printf`
- W3C `traceparent` header is propagated on all inbound and outbound HTTP calls
- Health endpoints `/health`, `/ready`, `/live` must always return correct status
- No global state — all dependencies injected via constructors
- Fail fast on misconfiguration — validate all env vars at startup

